                <h1>Diogo<br>Serino</h1>
                <p class="about-hero-role">
                    <span>Product Manager &amp; Builder</span>, founding-PM track, builds end-to-end
                </p>
                <p>I'm a Product Manager who builds and measures. I conceived and shipped <strong>TryCareerMatch</strong> end-to-end, from discovery and data model to UX and deployment. It's a free, no-signup career-discovery platform that maps 120+ skills to 60+ roles across 9 sectors.</p>
                <p>As a Financial Analyst at ABB Imobiliária, I didn't just read dashboards. I built them. Power BI, Python, SQL and KPI frameworks across a multi-company group, where my dashboards replaced manual reports and became the primary tool for investment decisions.</p>
                <p>Seven years of design give me a UX instinct and fast prototyping. I'm looking for a <strong>Founding PM / Product Manager</strong> role, remote-first, where building, data, and design aren't separate departments but one mindset.</p>
